---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Cookie Policy — HyperLog">
  <Header />
  <main class="flex-grow pt-24">
    <section class="py-16 px-6 bg-surface-base">
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto prose-invert">
        <p class="section-label text-secondary mb-4">Legal</p>
        <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white mb-2 tracking-tight">Cookie Policy</h1>
        <p class="text-xs text-outline/50 mb-10">Last updated: April 2026</p>

        <div class="space-y-8 text-sm text-secondary leading-relaxed">

          <div>
            <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-white mb-3">1. Introduction</h2>
            <p>This Cookie Policy explains how JetLink Technologies Ltd. ("JetLink", "we", "us", or "our") uses cookies and similar technologies on hyperlog.aero. HyperLog is a product developed and operated by JetLink Technologies Ltd. A cookie is a small text file placed on your device when you visit a website. Cookies can help websites remember your preferences, understand how visitors use the site, and improve functionality.</p>
          </div>

          <div>
            <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-white mb-3">2. How We Use Cookies</h2>
            <p>We currently use cookies for the following purposes:</p>
            <ul class="list-disc pl-5 mt-2 space-y-1">
              <li>To remember your cookie consent preferences</li>
              <li>If you choose to accept analytics cookies, to enable Google Analytics</li>
            </ul>
            <p class="mt-2">We do not use Google Analytics cookies unless you actively consent through our cookie banner.</p>
          </div>

          <div>
            <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-white mb-3">3. Strictly Necessary Cookie</h2>
            <p>We use a localStorage item (cookie-consent) to remember the choice you make in our cookie banner. This is used so that you are not repeatedly asked the same cookie question on every page visit, and so that we can remember whether you accepted or rejected analytics cookies.</p>
          </div>

          <div>
            <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-white mb-3">4. Analytics Cookies</h2>
            <p>If you click Accept on our cookie banner, we use Google Analytics cookies to help us understand how visitors use our website. These cookies may collect information such as pages viewed, approximate location, device and browser information, and interactions with the website. This information helps us analyse website traffic and improve the site. You can refuse these cookies by selecting Decline on our cookie banner, and you can change your choice later using our cookie settings controls.</p>
          </div>

          <div>
            <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-white mb-3">5. Managing Cookies</h2>
            <p>You can manage your cookie preferences at any time through our cookie controls in the website footer. You can also use your browser settings to block or delete cookies, although doing so may affect how some websites function.</p>
          </div>

          <div>
            <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-white mb-3">6. Cookie Table</h2>
            <div class="overflow-x-auto">
              <table class="w-full text-xs border-collapse">
                <thead>
                  <tr class="border-b border-outline-variant/20">
                    <th class="text-left py-3 pr-4 text-white font-bold">Cookie / Tool</th>
                    <th class="text-left py-3 pr-4 text-white font-bold">Purpose</th>
                    <th class="text-left py-3 pr-4 text-white font-bold">Type</th>
                    <th class="text-left py-3 pr-4 text-white font-bold">Duration</th>
                    <th class="text-left py-3 text-white font-bold">Consent</th>
                  </tr>
                </thead>
                <tbody>
                  <tr class="border-b border-outline-variant/10">
                    <td class="py-3 pr-4 font-mono text-on-surface-variant">cookie-consent</td>
                    <td class="py-3 pr-4">Remembers your cookie preference</td>
                    <td class="py-3 pr-4">Strictly necessary</td>
                    <td class="py-3 pr-4">Persistent</td>
                    <td class="py-3">No</td>
                  </tr>
                  <tr class="border-b border-outline-variant/10">
                    <td class="py-3 pr-4 font-mono text-on-surface-variant">_ga</td>
                    <td class="py-3 pr-4">Google Analytics — distinguishes users</td>
                    <td class="py-3 pr-4">Analytics</td>
                    <td class="py-3 pr-4">2 years</td>
                    <td class="py-3">Yes</td>
                  </tr>
                  <tr>
                    <td class="py-3 pr-4 font-mono text-on-surface-variant">_ga_*</td>
                    <td class="py-3 pr-4">Google Analytics 4 — session state</td>
                    <td class="py-3 pr-4">Analytics</td>
                    <td class="py-3 pr-4">2 years</td>
                    <td class="py-3">Yes</td>
                  </tr>
                </tbody>
              </table>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div>
            <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-white mb-3">7. Contact</h2>
            <p>If you have any questions about our use of cookies, please contact:</p>
            <p class="mt-2">JetLink Technologies Ltd.<br />Company No. 17100204<br />Level 9, Berkeley Square House<br />Berkeley Square, London W1J 6BY<br />United Kingdom<br />Email: <a href="mailto:info@hyperlog.aero" class="text-primary hover:text-white">info@hyperlog.aero</a></p>
          </div>

        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
  <Footer />
</BaseLayout>
